metadata.name: VANDA NFT #1
metadata.description: 60 unique Vanda NFT will launch alongside an exclusive Limited Edt Singapore Forum boxset. Be part of this exclusive club and redeem your physical collectible! Check the ‘PROPERTIES’ tab of the VANDA NFT Collection to find out the different traits attached to each NFT. The shoe size and availability of the box set are indicated so please check before purchasing. Full details on: Limitededt.com/vandanft
